title: Wild Card Weekend Recap
itunes:title: Wild Card Weekend Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal recap everything you need to know and more about wild card weekend including Wess attempting to say "lock apocalypse" (2:29). The Eagles win in an upset over the team of ATL (2:45), the Ravens face some adversity for their QB choice (15:06) and Zeke Elliot put this Cowboys team on his back. (29:10). Andrew Luck and the Colts march forward, but do they have what it takes to beat the Chiefs? (42:32).
